🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept n and find sum and average of first n numbers


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE sum_avg(n INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    sum_val INT := 0;
    avg_val FLOAT;
    i INT;
BEGIN
    FOR i IN 1..n LOOP
        sum_val := sum_val + i;
    END LOOP;

    avg_val := sum_val::FLOAT / n;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Sum = %', sum_val;
    RAISE NOTICE 'Average = %', avg_val;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL sum_avg(10);


